{"tid":2515192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"C君每月輸血續命 自幼遭母親拋棄 感激DJ老婆給他一個家：單戀咗佢十幾年","createTime":"2021-05-03T20:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:45:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"718e369aeb4438a0414b150eac8bc44a56e3059e","tid":2515192,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T20:57:11.000Z","msg":"農夫的C君（鄭詩君）近年帶給觀眾不少歡樂，但他的成長其實相當悲慘，四、五歲時，媽媽拋夫棄子，他跟爸爸相依為命。<br />\n<br />\n由於患有地中海貧血，8歲起就要自己打針，雖然現在仍然要每個月返醫院輸血，但自從前年跟港台DJ黃天頤結婚，他不再孤單，人生圓滿了。<br />\n<br />\n「我單戀咗佢十幾年，一拍拖就希望可以開花結果。有一日我瞓醒，睡眼惺忪之間，見到佢擦牙，我突然間覺得好幸福。其實就係要咁啫，就係要每日起身都見到佢。」37歲C君幸福人夫宣言。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_784940_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_784940_0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGniukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e6d04d90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_784940_0&h=93214810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_784940_0</a>"},{"pid":"37bdc10fed9dcaa20c1f6f1ea7a6a9e290bc8d09","tid":2515192,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T21:19:04.000Z","msg":"勁，溝到女神"},{"pid":"9359e680af1c48cb83dd7a22e1621db5079dc3c3","tid":2515192,"uid":158598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T21:22:13.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔知, 平時都係睇佢攪笑, 原來人後有咁堅強一面"},{"pid":"7cec6d9306fafb66136f150f67d9d05352cd5f31","tid":2515192,"uid":32667,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37bdc10fed9dcaa20c1f6f1ea7a6a9e290bc8d09","tid":2515192,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T21:19:04.000Z","msg":"勁，溝到女神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T22:15:01.000Z","msg":"通常個啲所謂女神都係第n*n手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b257700973ed9ef618d4f82d147ebed3b7dc99","tid":2515192,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37bdc10fed9dcaa20c1f6f1ea7a6a9e290bc8d09